It is believed that the men followed the driver home after he picked up his family at OR Tambo International Airport.In the video a man dressed in a grey hoodie is seen walking up to the driver's side as the car pulls up and threatening the driver with a gun. Two other robbers emerge helping the first suspect to empty the car and the trailer.The four-minute video shows the family being robbed of their belongings including their luggage. While in a separate video taken on the same property the three men can be seen climbing into a silver 2016 model Hyundai Accent before speeding off.- TMG Digital